                                gemeinnützige Organisationen" stellen
                                <a href="https://www.google.com/intl/de_ch/earth/outreach/grants/software/mapsapi.html">(link)</a>.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="frame-row">
                        <div class="frame-logo">
                            <img src="{{ asset('images/about/opensource_logo.gif') }}" alt="Open Source Logo"
                                 height="38" width="44"/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="frame-left">
                            {{ include(
                            'TixiApiBundle:Home:gpl_license.html.twig'
                            ) }}
